Class World

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmb.WORLD.worlds.world.World
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable<java.lang.String>
    public class World
extends java.lang.Object
implements Identifiable<java.lang.String>
    Author:
    oskar
    A BlockMap is a representation of ingame 2D voxel map.
    To load the map, create and the use the saveLoad module
    ,its getLoaded() method for getting loaded BlockMap
    ,its load() method to load data
    and at first setName() to set target name
